Subject: [PATCH 19/24] web-app: buttonify About dialog links with
 settings-style buttons

Replace the plain text links and footer actions in the About dialog with
SettingsIconButton rows, matching the Settings view. The links group
(SlothfulChat on GitHub, Delta Chat website) carries an open_in_new
indicator to signal they leave the app; Changelog and Imprint (both
local pages served alongside the app) and Help/View Log do not. Adds
buttons for the SlothfulChat GitHub repo and the changelog viewer we
ship at /changelog/, replacing the old link to GitHub releases.
